Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.\NAll right. I wanted to cover that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:25:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So, we covered it.\NWe were talking about the limitation of
