Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.52,0:27:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's you can just tell they're pushing\Ntheir mind to to cross that threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.88,0:27:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they figure the harder you push the\Nmind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.32,0:27:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't do it by pushing mind\Nbecause mind is only capable of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.60,0:27:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about. It cannot know. The mind cannot\Nknow. It does not have the capacity. It
