Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.91,0:27:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To know is one thing. To know about is\Nanother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:28:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The limitation of the intellect then is\Nit knows about something
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is still being extraneous to the\Nessence of that which you're trying to
