Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.39,0:28:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,birdness.\NYou can know about birdness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.12,0:28:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a straight A in ornithology.\NSo I know about birds
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.32,0:28:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't really know birdness.\NSo when you realize that then you you're
