Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.55,0:28:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Most most spiritual humility is a\Nspiritual pose
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.36,0:29:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's the you know all humility comes\Nout of understanding the real.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.88,0:29:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you really understand the\Nlimitation of the intellect then you're
