Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.96,0:29:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of all time even though they hit 499 all\Nbelieved in God. Oh, Sir Isaac Newton,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.55,0:29:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great the great great scientific\Ngeniuses of time all believed in God. So
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.36,0:29:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize so the mature intellect\Nrealizes its own limitations. The
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,difficulty with science is it becomes\Nvery arrogant. doesn't realize its own
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.24,0:29:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,limitations. It doesn't realize it's\Nreally stupid intrinsically
