Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.24,0:29:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only know about but it cannot\Ntake you across the threshold to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get how do you cross that\Nbarrier? So the intellect attracts us to
